    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs like a dream, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to hit the road with you today. Come by and see it for yourself\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
