    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.2 Cayman S is a purist's specification, featuring the 3.4L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The mid-ship engine layout ensures a low polar moment of inertia for surgical turn-in, complemented by a hydraulic steering rack that provides unparalleled tactile feedback. Mechanically robust, the naturally aspirated powerplant exhibits strong compression and smooth valvetrain operation. The chassis remains composed with a well-sorted suspension, while the braking system retains its bite with ventilated rotors and multi-piston calipers. Presenting in solid driver condition, this vehicle offers the raw, mechanical engagement missing from modern EPS-equipped counterparts.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
