    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. There are a few tiny beauty marks here and there from normal use, but it still looks great and runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
